==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Drouth
<hw>Drouth</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Same as
<er>Drought</er>.</def> <rj><au>Sandys.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Another ill accident is <qex>drouth</qex> at the spindling of
corn.</q> <rj><qau>Bacon.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>One whose <qex>drouth</qex> [thirst],⟦br⟧
Yet scarce allayed, still eyes the current stream.</q>
<rj><qau>Milton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>In the dust and <qex>drouth</qex> of London life.</q>
<rj><qau>Tennyson.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Drouthy</ent>⟦br⟧
